 & Tools\" tab in your Awin account.<\/p><p>In order to create your affiliate link please click 'Links & Tools' located in your navigation bar. Then please click 'Link Builder'. When you choose the ‘link builder', select ‘Joined’ and then the desired advertiser from the ‘Advertiser’ dropdown - in this case Spotlight Oral Care IE<br\/>After that, paste the URL you wish to direct your audience to in the ‘Destination URL’ field and click 'Generate Link'.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0,"css_class":""},"blocks":{}}},"block_order":["text_THwWwW"]},"accordion_row_Ti7jqe":{"type":"_a-ext-accordion-row","name":"Accordion row","settings":{"heading":"During the Verification step Awin is asking for a verification code - how can I find it?","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","width":20},"blocks":{"text_Xi3EtB":{"type":"t-ext-text","name":"t:names.text","settings":{"text":"<p>In order for it to be active, your account needs to be verified by Awin. The platform offers 2 options: A verification step via a charge of €1 or a verification step via a verification code. Please feel free to use our verification code 72087346 - this will allow you to skip the bank details step.<\/p>","width":"100%","max_width":"none","alignment":"left","type_preset":"rte","font":"var(--font-body--family)","font_size":"1rem","line_height":"normal","letter_spacing":"normal","case":"none","wrap":"pretty","color":"var(--color-foreground)","background":false,"background_color":"#00000026","corner_radius":0,"padding-block-start":0,"padding-block-end":0,"padding-inline-start":0,"padding-inline-end":0,"css_class":""},"blocks":{}}},"block_ord